casebody.data:
No. 10-6751. Chris J. Jacobs, Petitioner v. Wisconsin. 562 U.S. 1089, 131 S. Ct. 796, 2010 U.S. LEXIS 9542.

178 L. Ed. 2d 528,

December 6, 2010.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeals of Wisconsin, District III, dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
